verbose_text: According to Manjamalai and Grace [XREF_BIBR], essential oil of Wedelia chinensis (Osbeck) increases both the level of catalase and glutathione peroxidase in the lung and liver tissues, whereas in the serum the level of catalase decreased on the 22nd day (2.32 +/- 0.016 Lung tissue 6.47 +/- 0.060 liver tissue, 0.94 +/- 0.007 serum).
